[{"id": 101, "project_id": 32, "role": "user", "content": "Hey, I need to create a netflix like system design, create an infra for that", "architecture_version": 1, "created_at": "2026-03-03T05:09:53"}, {"id": 102, "project_id": 32, "role": "assistant", "content": "Generated architecture v1 with 0 AWS services using 0 tool calls.

[
  {
    "name": "create_security_group",
    "parameters": {
      "sg_id": "main_sg",
      "label": "Main Security Group",
      "vpc_id": "vpc-default",
      "ingress_rules": [
        {
          "protocol": "tcp",
          "port_range": "80",
          "cidr": "0.0.0.0/0",
          "description": "Allow HTTP"
        },
        {
          "protocol": "tcp",
          "port_range": "443",
          "cidr": "0.0.0.0/0",
          "description": "Allow HTTPS"
        },
        {
          "protocol": "tcp",
          "port_range": "8080",
          "cidr": "10.0.0.0/16",
          "description": "Allow traffic from ALB to ECS containers"
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "create_load_balancer",
    "parameters": {
      "lb_id": "alb_main",
      "label": "Main Application Load Balancer",
      "type": "ALB",
      "internal": false,
      "listener_port": 80,
      "target_port": 8080,
      "health_check_path": "/health"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "create_ecs_service",
    "parameters": {
      "service_id": "video_service",
      "label": "Video Streaming Service",
      "cpu": 512,
      "memory": 1024,
      "container_port": 8080,
      "desired_count": 3,
      "image": "public.ecr.aws/yourrepo/video-service:latest"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "create_api_gateway",
    "parameters": {
      "gateway_id": "netflix_api",
      "label": "Netflix API",
      "api_type": "REST",
      "cors_enabled": true,
      "stage_name": "prod"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "create_lambda_function",
    "parameters": {
      "function_id": "auth_lambda",
      "label": "Auth Lambda",
      "runtime": "python3.9",
      "memory": 256,
      "timeout": 10,
      "handler": "auth.handler"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "create_lambda_function",
    "parameters": {
      "function_id": "catalog_lambda",
      "label": "Catalog Lambda",
      "runtime": "python3.9",
      "memory": 256,
      "timeout": 10,
      "handler": "catalog.handler"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "create_lambda_function",
    "parameters": {
      "function_id": "playback_lambda",
      "label": "Playback Lambda",
      "runtime": "python3.9",
      "memory": 256,
      "timeout": 10,
      "handler": "playback.handler"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "create_cloudfront_distribution",
    "parameters": {
      "cf_id": "cf_dist",
      "label": "Video CDN",
      "origin_domain": "alb_main-123456.us-east-1.elb.amazonaws.com",
      "default_ttl": 86400,
      "price_class": "PriceClass_100"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "create_route53_zone",
    "parameters": {
      "zone_id": "dns_zone",
      "label": "Streaming DNS Zone",
      "domain_name": "streaming.example.com",
      "is_private": false
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "create_global_accelerator",
    "parameters": {
      "ga_id": "ga_main",
      "label": "Global Accelerator for Netflix",
      "flow_logs_enabled": true
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "connect_services",
    "parameters": {
      "from_service_id": "alb_main",
      "to_service_id": "video_service",
      "relationship": "targets"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "connect_services",
    "parameters": {
      "from_service_id": "netflix_api",
      "to_service_id": "auth_lambda",
      "relationship": "integration"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "connect_services",
    "parameters": {
      "from_service_id": "netflix_api",
      "to_service_id": "catalog_lambda",
      "relationship": "integration"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "connect_services",
    "parameters": {
      "from_service_id": "netflix_api",
      "to_service_id": "playback_lambda",
      "relationship": "integration"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "connect_services",
    "parameters": {
      "from_service_id": "ga_main",
      "to_service_id": "alb_main",
      "relationship": "endpoint"
    }
  },
  {
    "name": "connect_services",
    "parameters": {
      "from_service_id": "cf_dist",
      "to_service_id": "alb_main",
      "relationship": "origin"
    }
  }
]

**Summary**

- A default VPC security group (`main_sg`) allows HTTP/HTTPS inbound and traffic from the ALB to ECS containers.  
- An internet‑facing Application Load Balancer (`alb_main`) routes client traffic to the ECS Fargate service (`video_service`) that runs the video streaming container (3 tasks, 512 CPU/1 GB RAM each).  
- A REST API Gateway (`netflix_api`) exposes three Lambda functions (`auth_lambda`, `catalog_lambda`, `playback_lambda`) for authentication, catalog queries, and playback token generation.  
- A CloudFront distribution (`cf_dist`) caches video content, using the ALB as its origin, providing low‑latency global delivery.  
- Route 53 hosted zone (`dns_zone`) is created for the domain `streaming.example.com`.  
- AWS Global Accelerator (`ga_main`) fronts the ALB to improve global performance and reliability.  

All services are connected appropriately, forming a scalable, serverless‑friendly architecture suitable for a Netflix‑style video streaming platform.", "architecture_version": 1, "created_at": "2026-03-03T05:09:53"}]

